longBusinessSummary: Emo Capital Corp. operates as a carbon farming company. It is involved in the carbon sequestration business, including carbon sink farms/ranches activities; and development and sale of organic fertilizers, biochar, and carbon credit transactions. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
